@startuml AgentStore-Cohort-Workstreams
!theme plain
title AgentStore — Student Cohort Workstreams
caption How two TechX cohorts contribute to one marketplace

skinparam shadowing false
skinparam rectangleBorderColor #1a1a2e

rectangle "AgentStore MVP" as MVP #f8f9fc {

  rectangle "LLM Cohort" as LLM #fef3c7 {
    card "Agent manifests" as M1
    card "Tool manifests" as M2
    card "Prompt templates" as M3
    card "Agent runner" as M4
    card "Tool-call traces" as M5
    card "MCP simulation" as M6
  }

  rectangle "Data Science Cohort" as DS #fce7f3 {
    card "Trending algorithm" as D1
    card "Rating aggregation" as D2
    card "Review sentiment" as D3
    card "Quality scoring" as D4
    card "Usage analytics" as D5
    card "Recommendations" as D6
  }

  rectangle "Full Stack\n(both cohorts)" as FS #eef2ff {
    card "Frontend UI" as F1
    card "Backend API" as F2
    card "JSON storage" as F3
    card "Tests" as F4
  }
}

LLM --> FS : manifests &\nrunner logic
DS --> FS : scores &\ntrending data
FS --> MVP : integrated\ndemo

note as KanbanNote
  All work flows through
  **Kanban tickets** → branches → PRs
  Ticket prefix: **AS-XX**
end note

KanbanNote .. MVP

@enduml
